      <title>Hugo博客添加代码框复制功能</title>
      <link>https://mineguai.com/blog/hugo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%A1%86%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/</link>
